      <body>
         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Letter to the Herald of Arms ¶ Oberstudienrath Stälin ¶ Your Honour ¶  ¶ It is known from the announcement in the  ¶ Staatsanzeiger ¶  that His Majesty the King in consequence of the decision of 6 Jul...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">M71.12.18</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>From Johann von Wächter to Christoph Friedrich von Stälin</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">Bestand E 56 Bü. 28, Haupsstaatsarchiv, Stuttgart.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Letter not found. MS is a draft.</p>
               </note>[...] Schr. an den Wappencensor</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">Oberstudienrath Stälin</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">d. d. 18 Dbr 1871.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">E Hochw</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>ist aus der im Staatsanzeiger erfolgten Veröffentlichung bekannt dass S. Maj. der König vermöge H. Entschliessung v. 6. Juli d. J. den Direktor des botan. u. zoologischen Gartens zu Melbourne in Australien Herrn Dr. von Müller in den erbl. Freiherrnstand zu erheben gnädigst geruht haben.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ich habe nun dem Freiherrn von Müller zunächst ersucht mir seine Wünsche in Betreff des ihm zu ertheilenden Wappens mitzutheilen. An Folge dessen hat mir derselbe den hier angeschlossenen Entwurf eines Wappens mit dem Bemerken übermacht, dass er es meinem Ermessen überlasse die durch die Heraldik etwa gebotenen Aenderungen vorzunehmen.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Bezüglich d. Wappen<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Ueber die <seg style="font-style: italic; ">deleted and replaced with marginal insertion</seg> Bezüglich d. Wappen.</p>
               </note> Farben hat<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">hat <seg style="font-style: italic; ">above</seg> welche <seg style="font-style: italic; ">deleted</seg>.</p>
               </note> Brn Müller<note xml:id="ftn4" type="footnote" n="4">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">auf seinem Wappen wünscht hat derselbe <seg style="font-style: italic; ">deleted after</seg> Müller.</p>
               </note> keinen Wunsch geäussert. Ich ersuche nun E. Hochw. eine Skizze des Brn Müller zu ertheilenden Wappens unter Berücksichtigung seiner Wünsche, soweit dies nach den Regeln der Heraldik thunlich erscheint gef. zu entwerfen<note xml:id="ftn5" type="footnote" n="5">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">zu wollen <seg style="font-style: italic; ">deleted after</seg> entwerfen.</p>
               </note> und mir behufs der Mittheilung an Brn Müller zukommen lassen zu wollen —</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">Mit …</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>W<note xml:id="ftn6" type="footnote" n="6">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Wächter's initial.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Letter to the Herald of Arms</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Oberstudienrath Stälin</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Your Honour</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>It is known from the announcement in the <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Staatsanzeiger</seg>
               <note xml:id="ftn7" type="footnote" n="7">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <seg style="">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                     </seg>
                     <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Staats-Anzeiger für Württemberg</seg>
                     <seg style="">, no. 118, 18 July 1871.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note> that His Majesty the King in consequence of the decision of 6 July this year has graciously deigned to raise the Director of the botanical and zoological garden at Melbourne in Australia Dr von Mueller to the hereditary rank of baron.<note xml:id="ftn8" type="footnote" n="8">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <seg style="">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Karl I, King of W</seg>ü<seg style="">rttemberg, to M, 6 July 1871.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I have now first of all requested Baron von Mueller to tell me his wishes in respect to the coat of arms to be granted to him.<note xml:id="ftn9" type="footnote" n="9">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <seg style="">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>J. von W</seg>ä<seg style="">chter to M, 12 July 1871.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note> As a consequence he has transmited a design enclosed here with the remark that he leaves it to my judgement to make the changes perchance prescribed by heraldry.<note xml:id="ftn10" type="footnote" n="10">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <seg style="">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>M to J. von W</seg>ä<seg style="">chter, 8 October 1971 (in this edition as 71-10-08a).</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>With reference to the colours of the arms Baron Mueller has expressed no wish. I now request your honour kindly to draft a sketch of the arms granted to Baron Mueller considering his wishes as far as possible according to the rules of heraldry and to send me for the purpose of communication to Baron Mueller.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">With ….</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>W.<note xml:id="ftn11" type="footnote" n="11">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <seg style="">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>See C. F. von St</seg>ählin to J. von Wächter, 4 January 1872 (in this edition as M72-01-04).</p>
               </note>
            </p>
         </div>
      </body>
